text: BING NEWS: Vinatieri's field goals leads Colts past Jaguars 16-13 in OT INDIANAPOLIS (AP) — Adam Vinatieri kicked a 27-yard field goal with 4:36 left in overtime to give the Colts a 16-13 victory over Jacksonville — and an NFL record-tying 15th consecutive win over a division opponent.
